{"tid":573408,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳中心現「天空之鏡」　網民憂女士走光","createTime":"2018-02-26T12:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T14:42:26.000Z","uid":150685,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ce6e5e3b8a83bd6bbdadff096adeff1e2929ebd3","tid":573408,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180226/s00001/2e6c14539ce8d4c65147eb9a0c2c7d07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180226%2Fs00001%2F2e6c14539ce8d4c65147eb9a0c2c7d07.jpg&h=ad152e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少穿裙子的女性外出都會做足保護措施，以免走光，但即使如此，不少地方的地板設計卻讓人防不勝防。<br />\n<br />\n有網友在fb「將軍澳」群組上載一幅在將軍澳中心所攝照片，當中可見商場部分十分光亮，甚至能將天花板清楚反映。網友憂慮女士若走在這種地板上，很容易走光，呼籲穿裙子的女性小心。<br />\n<br />\n照片上載後惹起網民熱議，有網民笑指不必去南美玻利維亞便能觀賞到「天空之鏡」；有人表示這名網友少見多怪，稱本港不少商場皆是如此設計，甚至每晚都有工人打蠟；又有網民批評無事生非「搵嚟嘈」，在香港男性間製造「白色恐怖」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180226/s00001/1519637477472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180226%2Fs00001%2F1519637477472&d=IJnNHdeO5SHS6%2FwiWg0FZfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=3d841104\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180226%2Fs00001%2F1519637477472&h=d1fdc382\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180226/s00001/1519637477472</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7e786e6f9dc0d5449d37dd9a8eb87004d8ec16","tid":573408,"uid":36964,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T12:30:41.000Z","msg":"Dup低頭就裝裙底，正面望就視姦，望天花睇唔到路撞到就叫非禮，香港做男人慘過狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hk